biography: Sieer is an experienced founder, serial entrepreneur and Managing Director with a demonstrated history of working in the information technology and services industry. He is a specialised and strong business development professional with a Master of Science (M.Sc.) focused in Geography, Geo-Eingineering, Geo-IT and Political Science from Ruprecht-Karls-Universität Heidelberg.
